</td></tr><tr><td style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">2.0.0</td><td style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">May 2025</td><td style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;">IHO CL xx/2025</td><td style="border-top:none;mso-border-top-alt:none;border-bottom:solid windowtext 1.5pt;mso-border-bottom-alt:solid windowtext 1.5pt;page-break-after:auto;"><p style="page-break-after:auto" class="MsoNormal"><a name="_59662741-d730-6d3f-9992-734e8064de68" id="_59662741-d730-6d3f-9992-734e8064de68"></a>First operational version of S-128</p>
